THIRD-PARTY TEST ATTRIBUTION
=============================

The following test files contain test cases adapted from Microsoft's
Visual Studio Code (Code - OSS) repository:

  https://github.com/microsoft/vscode

VSCode Source Files Referenced
------------------------------

  test_vscode_cursor_movement.py   ← cursor.test.ts
  test_vscode_text_editing.py      ← cursor.test.ts
  test_vscode_selection.py         ← cursor.test.ts
  test_vscode_undo_redo.py         ← cursor.test.ts
  test_vscode_word_movement.py     ← wordOperations.test.ts
  test_vscode_word_selection.py    ← wordOperations.test.ts
  test_vscode_multicursor.py       ← multicursor.test.ts
  test_vscode_find_replace.py      ← findModel.test.ts
  test_vscode_case_transform.py    ← linesOperations.test.ts
  test_vscode_sort_lines.py        ← sortLinesCommand.test.ts
  test_vscode_move_lines.py        ← moveLinesCommand.test.ts

These tests were NOT copied verbatim. The test intent and assertions were
adapted from TypeScript/Mocha to Python/pytest, with 1-based positions
converted to 0-based and Textual Pilot API used in place of DOM events.

